title: Grateful Dead Live at Richfield Coliseum on 1991-09-05
description:
Set I
Mississippi Half Step Uptown Toodleloo
Little Red Rooster
Stagger Lee
Queen Jane Approximately
Ramble On Rose
Cassidy
Don't Ease Me In
Set II
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider >
Man Smart (Woman Smarter) >
Ship of Fools >
Truckin' >
Smokestack Lightning >
Drums >
Space >
I Need A Miracle >
Black Peter >
Sugar Magnolia

Encore:
U.S. Blues


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Vince Welnick - Keyboards
Bruce Hornsby - Piano, Accordion
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
